@startuml
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ArrowColor #334155
skinparam participantPadding 20

title 权限与路由协作图

actor 用户
participant "登录页\n/login" as LoginPage
participant "Pinia Auth Store" as AuthStore
participant "Vue Router Guard" as RouterGuard
participant "Auth API" as AuthApi
participant "AuthController" as AuthController
participant "SecurityConfig / JWT" as Security
database "sys_user" as DB

用户 -> LoginPage : 输入账号密码
LoginPage -> AuthApi : POST /api/v1/auth/login
AuthApi -> AuthController : 登录请求
AuthController -> Security : 认证与签发 token
Security -> DB : 查询用户与角色
DB --> Security : 返回用户信息
Security --> AuthController : token + user
AuthController --> AuthApi : ApiResponse.ok(...)
AuthApi --> AuthStore : 保存 token / user / permissions
用户 -> RouterGuard : 访问受保护路由
RouterGuard -> AuthStore : 检查 token / user / homePath
RouterGuard -> AuthApi : 必要时 GET /api/v1/auth/me
RouterGuard --> 用户 : 按角色跳转教师或学生首页

@enduml
